super-duper nitpick again: this is a static value, that it doesn't appear to be used outside of this module.

Make this

```scala
object ActiveJson {
  private val activeJsonPath =
    RelativePath("project").resolve("target").resolve("active.json")

  def apply(cwd: AbsolutePath): AbsolutePath =
    cwd.resolve(activeJsonPath)
 
  def unapply(path: Path): Boolean = {
    path.endsWith(activeJsonPath.toNIO) &&
      path.toFile.isFile
  }
```

